description.narrative: In 2021, UNICEF support to the Lao Government was instrumental in adopting the vision paper “Core Recommendations for Strengthening the Child Protection System” based on the findings from the Assessment of the Child Protection System in Lao PDR. To implement it, the National Strategic Guidelines for Social Service Workforce Development and the National Plan of Action (NPA) on Child Protection; System Strengthening 2022-2026 were developed (under finalization). Other documents launched in 2021 with UNICEF help are the NPA on Mothers and Children and the NPA on Violence against Women and Children 2021-2025. | Status:Met | As-of Date:16/12/2021
